fin applies immediately to variable interest entities created after january   and to variable interest entities in which an enterprise obtains an interest after that date 
it applies in the first fiscal year or interim period beginning after june   to variable interest entities in which an enterprise holds a variable interest that it acquired before february  the company is in the process of determining what impact  if any  the adoption of the provisions of fin will have upon its financial condition or results of operations 
